Bobertrons eyes opened. It seemed like for the first time. His body,(which wasin beast mode) looked weird. It was a hawk yet not. He spread his wings and flew outside. He soared above the base. The wind felt great in his hair. Hewas know a destron. Although he felt almost as a piece of him was missing. Bobertron landed. Boberton Destonize! Bobertron transformed into robot mode. He had two guns on each hand. A jet pack on his back. A cloaking button on his shoulder. And something else. It was a button that he was not sure what it did. He pressed, suddenly he felt odd  a large build up of energy built up inside him.He then released it it fires and vaporized a tree. This however seemed to almost to completly drain him.So he fell to the ground. His last thought was "kewl".
